Description: The skill counts the exact number of days, weeks, months, or years between today and any date in the past or future. Just ask "how long until 15-Nov" or "how many weeks since 1-Jan-2002".

Description: Malaysia Public Holidays let's you know upcoming holidays in Malaysia. This covers national and state holidays. For example, you can ask, "Alexa, ask my public holidays when is the next holiday", or "Alexa, ask my public holidays when is the next holiday in November". You can also ask, "Alexa, ask my public holidays list out all holidays in March".
Quote2: "Alexa, ask my public holidays when is the next public holiday in June."
Quote1: "Alexa, ask my public holidays when is the next public holiday."

Description: Bookmarker is a skill to save and retrieve the current page that you have just read. Just tell Alexa to request BookMarker to set the book mark page for the book that you have just read., you are all set. Give it a try.

Quote1: "Alexa Ask Bookmarker to set the bookmark to 150"

Description: Quote Maker is a development tool that allows developers to create notifications in real-time, and trigger the sending of SetIndicator directives to all Alexa-enabled devices connected to the associated Amazon account. When you ask Quote Maker to create a notification, a randomly selected quote is added to your notifications queue, and results in your device receiving a directive with instructions to persistently inform the user that a notification is available to be retrieved.
Quote2: "Alexa, ask Quote Maker to create a notification."

Description: Just ask for a quick reminder, and we'll send you a text at the time. This isn't a fancy reminder service with snoozing, repeating reminders, or any of that jazz. Just ask us, and we'll remind you. The skill works by securely storing your phone number and reminders associated with your unique Alexa userId. Then, when it's time for your reminder, we send your reminder to you via SMS. Standard text messaging rates from your carrier apply. Reminders will be sent from the number 37083.
Quote2: "Remind me to feed the dog in 10 minutes."
Quote1: "Alexa, ask My Extra Brain to Remind Me to wash the car on Saturday."

Description: With Mood Journal you can track your mood on a daily basis. Each day when you open the journal, simply tell Alexa how you feel, it then plays music based on your mood. Mood journal allows you to create one journal per day. You can tell mood journal how you feel using one word at a time. You can update an existing mood journal from any previous date as well as delete any old journals.
Quote2: "what was the entry on August second twenty sixteen"
Quote1: "Alexa, open mood journal and I am happy"

Description: The Holiday Freak skill tells you what National Holidays are being celebrated for the current day. Every day, there is at least one reason for all to celebrate. If you don't currently have a special occasion today, use the Holiday Freak skill to get one (or many!).

Quote1: "Alexa, ask Holiday Freak to give me today's holidays"

Description: Never have to judge if it's your recycling week by looking down the street. To use Recycling Reminder, ask Alexa to "ask Recycling Reminder if pickup is this week" to have a quick reminder or simply, "open Recycling Reminder".
Quote2: "Alexa, ask recycling reminder when my recycling is picked up"
Quote1: "Alexa, ask recycling reminder to remember my recycling week as this week"

Description: This Alexa Skill can keep track of the days that you drive for your carpool and remind you in the mornings. Description: Assist Reminder will help you remember where you have put any of your items. You can do this by telling Alexa to remember where you have put certain things. Then you can tell Alexa to remind you where you have put these things. For example, you could say, "Alexa, tell Assist Reminder I put my wallet on desk ". After which you can say "Alexa, ask Assist Reminder where is my wallet" and Alexa will tell you your wallet is on your desk. This is helpful for when you can not find your things, such as your badge, laptop, headphones, etc.
Quote2: "Alexa, ask Assist Reminder to list all"
Quote1: "Alexa, tell Assist Reminder I put my wallet in the desk."

Description: School Kit lets you keep track of the stuff your kids need for school. Add Games Kit for Thomas for Tuesday". You can add as many items you like for as many children as you have.

Description: This skill is designed to help you remember where you put your stuff. You can tell it where your stuff is and after you inevitably forget it, you can just ask Alexa. Unfortunately this is setup for a pretty strict input structure. For making an entry say something like "My/The/... stuff is/are in/at/under/... location", and for getting reminded the command structure is "where is/are my/the/... stuff". You can also delete entries. I hope this skill helps somebody.

The following skill is a demonstration of an IEEE conference suggestion engine, for IEEE members wondering about conferences they may attend during the coming months. The engine uses a list of conferences along with their topics and dates in the United States. A user can either search by a specific date, a specific month, a conference topic, or a state that a conference may be in. A user can also combine parameters, just as long as they are not a specific date and a month in one request.

"Alexa, ask i. triple e. conference suggester to show me conferences about p...
    "
